00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:01,640
find this evil mastermind.

284
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,880
But…

285
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:05,480
What's wrong?

286
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:07,880
But this nursery rhyme adopts the tune

287
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:09,240
of the song newly composed

288
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:12,320
and performed by Mr. Jin
at the Winter Solstice feast

289
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:14,520
at Prince Xian's mansion.

290
00:18:14,520 --> 00:18:16,712
"Joy and Sorrow".

291
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:23,880
I beg for your discernment.

292
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:25,160
I composed this piece,

293
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:28,040
inspired by the Winter Solstice.

294
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:29,760
Indeed, it was first performed

295
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:31,640
at the feast,

296
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:33,960
but it did not have lyrics,

297
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:37,000
let alone disloyal intentions.

298
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:38,240
What if the listeners

299
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,520
harbored ill will

300
00:18:39,520 --> 00:18:40,960
although the player didn't?

301
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:42,720
The last line of that nursery rhyme says,

302
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:43,880
"The old lady frowns upon it.

303
00:18:43,880 --> 00:18:45,120
Salt shall rise."

304
00:18:45,120 --> 00:18:46,760
"Salty" sounds just like "Xian".

305
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:49,320
I'm afraid it refers to Prince Xian.

306
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:56,000
Summon Prince Xuan.

307
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:02,000
Mother Empress.

308
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,280
I am unaware of it.

309
00:19:03,280 --> 00:19:04,360
I am innocent.

310
00:19:04,360 --> 00:19:08,040
I first heard "Joy and Sorrow"
on the feast and paid no further attention

311
00:19:08,040 --> 00:19:09,160
to it.

312
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,160
I had no idea that

313
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:12,000
someone would compose lyrics

314
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,800
to insinuate you.

315
00:19:13,800 --> 00:19:14,960
I don't believe

316
00:19:14,960 --> 00:19:16,400
it was done by Mr. Jin

317
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:18,600
or instigated by Prince Xian.

318
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:20,120
But Mr. Jin just performed

319
00:19:20,120 --> 00:19:22,200
the song at Prince Xian's mansion,

320
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:23,480
and someone immediately spread it

321
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:25,360
with disrespectful lyrics.

322
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:26,920
What's more,

323
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:28,680
the ending line implies

324
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:32,560
that Prince Xian is seeking greater power.

325
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:37,080
Please discern the truth.

326
00:19:37,080 --> 00:19:39,120
Someone is using this nursery rhyme

327
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:40,960
to sow discord between you and me

328
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:44,080
and even to kill me, Mother Empress.

329
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:45,280
Empress Dowager.

330
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:46,960
Seditious words bewitch the people.

331
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:48,000
If we allow this

332
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,280
to carry on,

333
00:19:49,280 --> 00:19:50,280
it would at least

334
00:19:50,280 --> 00:19:51,800
harm Prince Xian and Mr. Jin.

335
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:53,320
At worst, people with evil intentions

336
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:54,320
may accuse Prince Xian

337
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:56,840
of plotting a usurpation.

338
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:03,960
Empress Dowager, please allow me

339
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:05,040
to arrest all the guests

340
00:20:05,040 --> 00:20:07,080
at the feast in Prince Xian's mansion

341
00:20:07,080 --> 00:20:09,240
for a thorough investigation.

342
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:16,160
This matter

343
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:19,920
arose from the feast

344
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:22,520
held by Prince Xian.

345
00:20:22,520 --> 00:20:24,240
From now on,

346
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:26,720
Prince Xian, Xiao Zhong,

347
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:29,560
will be placed under house arrest.

348
00:20:29,560 --> 00:20:31,680
Jinzang, who composed the song,

349
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:35,800
shall await trial under the custody
of the Imperial Inspectorate.

350
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:41,080
The other musicians who attended the banquet

351
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:43,640
shall be investigated by

352
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:46,696
the Imperial Inspectorate.

353
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:51,112
Yes, Your Majesty.

354
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:06,000
Great Chief, Madam.

355
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:08,440
Madam Xu sent a confidential letter.

356
00:21:17,520 --> 00:21:19,520
What happened?

357
00:21:23,080 --> 00:21:24,200
Things changed last night.

358
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:25,440
Be very careful.

359
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:26,600
Don't let the Shen and Yan families

360
00:21:26,600 --> 00:21:28,960
go through what had happened.

361
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:31,000
Help!

362
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:32,280
- Go.
- Help!

363
00:21:32,280 --> 00:21:33,560
Save me, master.

364
00:21:33,560 --> 00:21:35,120
Master, save me.

365
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:36,440
Hurry up.

366
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,560
Get Liuniang.

367
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:38,800
Get Great Chief.

368
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:39,880
Find Liuniang

369
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:41,240
and the Great Chief.

370
00:21:41,240 --> 00:21:43,846
Hurry up!

371
00:21:43,846 --> 00:21:44,880
[Yan Mansion]

372
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:46,320
Find them

373
00:21:46,320 --> 00:21:48,160
to help me!

374
00:21:48,160 --> 00:21:50,880
Hurry. Inform Liuniang.

375
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:52,840
Hurry. Close the door.

376
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:55,400
Close the door.

377
00:22:03,760 --> 00:22:06,152
Get in.

378
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:18,888
Zang.

379
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:21,080
What happened?

380
00:22:21,080 --> 00:22:23,360
My sister.

381
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:26,184
Zang.

382
00:22:27,320 --> 00:22:29,520
What happened?

383
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:31,440
- Go.
- Zang.

384
00:22:31,440 --> 00:22:34,120
- Hurry up. Behave.
- No.

385
00:22:34,120 --> 00:22:35,560
- No.
- Go.

386
00:22:35,560 --> 00:22:38,000
- Zang.
- Hurry up.

387
00:22:50,760 --> 00:22:51,840
Father.

388
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:52,880
What happened?

389
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,160
Why did they arrest my mother?

390
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:56,120
Liuniang, your mother was arrested by

391
00:22:56,120 --> 00:22:57,280
the Imperial Inspectorate.

392
00:22:57,280 --> 00:22:58,320
Your uncle Jinzang is accused

393
00:22:58,320 --> 00:23:00,040
of colluding with Prince Xian for a usurpation

394
00:23:00,040 --> 00:23:02,000
and the whole clan will be implicated.

395
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,520
My uncle is just a musician.

396
00:23:03,520 --> 00:23:04,840
How could he plot a usurpation?

397
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:06,800
No way. It's a setup.

398
00:23:06,800 --> 00:23:08,640
Liuniang, calm down.

399
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:10,440
Lady Jin may have been arrested,

400
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:13,440
but the Yan family hasn't been implicated.

401
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:14,560
The Imperial Inspectorate

402
00:23:14,560 --> 00:23:15,560
wouldn't

403
00:23:15,560 --> 00:23:17,560
go after you just yet.

404
00:23:17,560 --> 00:23:20,200
The Yan family hasn't been implicated.

405
00:23:20,800 --> 00:23:21,920
That's right, Father.

406
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:23,160
Mother is from the Jin family,

407
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:25,360
but she has married into the Yan family.

408
00:23:25,360 --> 00:23:28,000
It shouldn't have affected her.

409
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:31,000
They have no reason to arrest her.

410
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:37,760
Those people are like

411
00:23:37,760 --> 00:23:39,800
the soul reapers from the underworld.

412
00:23:39,800 --> 00:23:41,440
How can we reason with them?

413
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:42,480
They just arrest

414
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:44,800
whoever they want to arrest.

415
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:47,920
No.

416
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:50,000
It's not that they are unreasonable.

417
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:53,240
You didn't dare to reason with them, did you?

418
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:55,480
Father, Mother.

419
00:23:55,480 --> 00:23:56,520
You let the Imperial Inspectorate

420
00:23:56,520 --> 00:23:58,440
arrest my mother for no reason,

421
00:23:58,440 --> 00:23:59,680
without stepping up

422
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:02,360
to ask a question, right?

423
00:24:09,080 --> 00:24:10,680
Fine.

424
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:12,400
You all fear the Black Fiend.

425
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:15,120
I don't. I'll save her if you don't.

426
00:24:15,120 --> 00:24:18,120
Liuniang.

427
00:24:18,120 --> 00:24:20,488
Liuniang.

428
00:24:30,016 --> 00:24:31,280
Liuniang.

429
00:24:31,280 --> 00:24:33,240
Chuichui.

430
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:35,080
There you are.

431
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:36,120
The Great Chief

432
00:24:36,120 --> 00:24:38,080
sent Jing Lin to convey the message that

433
00:24:38,080 --> 00:24:39,760
he would meet with the Empress Dowager

434
00:24:39,760 --> 00:24:42,400
to plead for the Jin family.

435
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:44,120
Stiffy Jiang and I split up to look for you.

436
00:24:44,120 --> 00:24:46,880
I thought I could find you here.

437
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:50,080
Chuichui, thank you.

438
00:24:50,080 --> 00:24:51,800
But Prince Xian is involved.

439
00:24:51,800 --> 00:24:52,800
It's very tricky.

440
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:54,560
It's not enough to have Shen Du's help.

441
00:24:54,560 --> 00:24:57,760
Go back first. I'll meet Prime Minister Zhang.

442
00:24:57,760 --> 00:25:00,680
Okay, be careful.

443
00:25:24,120 --> 00:25:26,280
Stiffy Jiang, is that you?

444
00:25:31,880 --> 00:25:34,344
Lai Luozhi.

445
00:25:41,360 --> 00:25:43,320
Are you disappointed

446
00:25:43,320 --> 00:25:45,680
that it's me?

447
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:46,800
I…

448
00:25:46,800 --> 00:25:48,480
I have a date with Jiang Langxing.

449
00:25:48,480 --> 00:25:50,720
He will be coming soon.

450
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:52,600
Jiang Langxing.

451
00:25:52,600 --> 00:25:55,160
Jiang Langxing.

452
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:57,200
Is he the only one

453
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:59,520
you care about now?

454
00:26:07,080 --> 00:26:09,000
So obedient.

455
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:11,336
How nice.

456
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:26,360
The Chief Director of the Ministry of Justice

457
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:28,920
is here to meet Prime Minister Zhang.

458
00:26:30,080 --> 00:26:32,840
Mrs. Shen, our lord is not home today.

459
00:26:32,840 --> 00:26:34,240
I have asked around.

460
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:35,520
He's shut himself in

461
00:26:35,520 --> 00:26:37,080
ever since what happened.

462
00:26:37,080 --> 00:26:39,680
He didn't even go to court today.

463
00:26:41,120 --> 00:26:42,800
The Chief Director of the Ministry of Justice,

464
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:44,360
[Zhang Mansion]
wife of the Great Chief,

465
00:26:44,360 --> 00:26:47,080
the sixth daughter of Mr. Yan,

466
00:26:47,080 --> 00:26:50,160
is here to meet Prime Minister Zhang.

467
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:52,760
Mrs. Shen, please don't
make things hard for us.

468
00:26:52,760 --> 00:26:54,240
I won't.

469
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:56,080
I will just wait here.

470
00:26:56,080 --> 00:26:57,320
In a day or two,

471
00:26:57,320 --> 00:26:59,720
he's bound to come out, right?

472
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:03,240
Surely, Prime Minister Zhang
wouldn't take the back door

473
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:04,880
or sneak through the dog hole

474
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:07,360
just to avoid me, right?

475
00:27:14,760 --> 00:27:16,840
I knew I couldn't

476
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:18,680
easily get rid of you.

477
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:20,600
If I do not come out,

478
00:27:20,600 --> 00:27:22,440
are you going to turn my mansion

479
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:24,880
upside down?

480
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:30,360
Prime Minister Zhang,
please save the Jin family.

481
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:36,960
Stop pushing me.

482
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:38,400
I can't help you

483
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:41,240
with what you're asking.

484
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:42,440
My lord,

485
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:43,840
you are the Prime Minister

486
00:27:43,840 --> 00:27:45,080
and the chief counselor.

487
00:27:45,080 --> 00:27:46,560
The Jin family suffers injustice.

488
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:48,040
You can't ignore this.

489
00:27:48,040 --> 00:27:51,040
Since you have the Empress Dowager's tablet,

490
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:54,240
why do you seek my help but not hers?

491
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:56,960
I am just a minor official

492
00:27:56,960 --> 00:27:59,680
to the Empress Dowager.

493
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,960
I would be

494
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:02,960
overestimating myself to believe that

495
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:05,680
I can interfere with court affairs.

496
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:08,960
Since you understand that,

497
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:10,160
then how come

498
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:11,920
you don't get why Lai Luozhi

499
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:15,600
is blaming this on Mr. Jin?

500
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:19,680
It's because of me?

501
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:21,720
This is happening because

502
00:28:21,720 --> 00:28:24,440
you are both married to Shen Du and working as

503
00:28:24,440 --> 00:28:25,520
the Chief Director

504
00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:26,680
of the Ministry of Justice

505
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:28,840
who keeps causing trouble.

506
00:28:28,840 --> 00:28:30,120
Of course.

507
00:28:30,120 --> 00:28:32,280
It's not just that.

508
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:33,360
It is said that

509
00:28:33,360 --> 00:28:34,760
on the night of the Winter Solstice,

510
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:37,680
Lai Luozhi reported to the Empress Dowager

511
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:40,680
that you were sent by me

512
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:42,560
to win over Shen Du

513
00:28:42,560 --> 00:28:45,520
and serve Prince Xian in the power struggle.

514
00:28:45,520 --> 00:28:47,840
Mr. Jin refuted him and defied

515
00:28:47,840 --> 00:28:51,720
the Empress Dowager right on the spot.

516
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:57,000
My uncle

517
00:28:57,640 --> 00:29:00,120
defied the Empress Dowager for me?

518
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:02,000
Our laws forbid

519
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:04,040
palace attendants and musicians

520
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:06,160
from discussing court affairs.

521
00:29:06,160 --> 00:29:08,280
Violation is met with the death penalty.

522
00:29:08,280 --> 00:29:10,200
But Jinzang

523
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,760
grew arrogant from favoritism.

524
00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:14,840
He overestimated himself.

525
00:29:14,840 --> 00:29:18,000
Uncle wasn't arrogant from favoritism.

526
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:20,560
Nor did he overestimate himself.

527
00:29:20,560 --> 00:29:22,600
He did that because he's my uncle.

528
00:29:22,600 --> 00:29:25,000
He sees me as his family.

529
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:26,520
He'd rather risk his life

530
00:29:26,520 --> 00:29:29,400
than see me in trouble.

531
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:31,040
Liuniang.

532
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:32,880
All these years,

533
00:29:32,880 --> 00:29:34,280
I've been using you people

534
00:29:34,280 --> 00:29:36,480
instead of caring for you.

535
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:37,800
But regarding this matter,

536
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:41,000
I've said all that can be said.

537
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:44,240
Between Prince Xian and the Jin family,

538
00:29:44,240 --> 00:29:48,280
I have no choice.

539
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:10,680
Back then,

540
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:12,560
were you faced with

541
00:30:12,560 --> 00:30:14,360
the same choices regarding

542
00:30:14,360 --> 00:30:16,920
the Shen family's case?

543
00:30:27,280 --> 00:30:29,576
My lord.

544
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:38,520
Prince Xian is under house arrest.

545
00:30:38,520 --> 00:30:41,320
And yet I've remained silent.

546
00:30:41,320 --> 00:30:43,280
Do you know why?

547
00:30:43,280 --> 00:30:45,280
No, I don't.

548
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:49,880
I've watched Prince Xian grow up.

549
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:52,360
My feelings for Prince Xian

550
00:30:52,360 --> 00:30:53,600
are just like those

551
00:30:53,600 --> 00:30:55,520
of Jinzang for Yan Xing.

552
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:58,360
Of course, I wish to risk myself

553
00:30:58,360 --> 00:31:01,200
to get Prince Xian out of this.

554
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:03,840
About the nursery rhyme,

555
00:31:03,840 --> 00:31:06,040
I know very well that

556
00:31:06,040 --> 00:31:09,240
Prince Xian has no heart for usurpation.

557
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:13,520
The Empress Dowager knows that as well.

558
00:31:14,760 --> 00:31:16,120
But she is not

559
00:31:16,120 --> 00:31:19,160
just a mother,

560
00:31:20,880 --> 00:31:22,520
but also the Empress Dowager

561
00:31:22,520 --> 00:31:24,680
of Dacang.

562
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:26,480
If I step forward,

563
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:27,960
then my disciples will

564
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:29,760
follow my footsteps

565
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:32,440
and file petitions to the Empress Dowager,

566
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:35,960
urging her to release Prince Xian.

567
00:31:38,840 --> 00:31:41,920
The more pressure we apply,

568
00:31:41,920 --> 00:31:46,694
the more we push Prince Xian to a dead end.

569
00:31:46,694 --> 00:31:50,160
[Ministry of Justice]

570
