662
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:08,480
and consider me a good friend?

663
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:09,560
Besides…

664
00:37:09,560 --> 00:37:11,640
Besides, our mothers
are buried in the same place.

665
00:37:11,640 --> 00:37:13,440
This is fate.

666
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:14,920
